title: Desi Arnaz AKA Ricky Ricardo - music from I Love Lucy
description:
Desi Arnaz AKA Ricky Ricardo - I think this is every song from the series that I could salvage without too much laugh track interference. Has the standards, and a few extras, Harpo Marx playing take me out to the ballgame on his harp, Bob Hope doing a baseball number with Ricky and Lucy. and many others.

please remember most of these were ripped from the show, so there are some laughs in the backround. its still a collection worth having for any I Love Lucy fan. Most of the files are .wma format.

Caring is Sharing. Be like Johnny AppleSEED
